## Minecraft Consoles Launcher

A launcher for MinecraftConsoles (https://github.com/smartcmd/MinecraftConsoles) — a PC port of "Minecraft Legacy Console Edition".

Handles installation, updates, and launching for both the game and the dedicated server, all from one place.

Places a shortcut on the users desktop to the launcher.

---

## Download

[Latest Release → Standalone_Legacy_Launcher] https://github.com/Lucario4LyfeYT/Minecraft-Consoles-Launcher/releases/tag/Standalone_Legacy_Launcher

> The standalone version does not require .net 8.0 to run. Bascially it works out of the "Box"

